{"tid":1057539,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國警告德國：若用華為設備將有代價","createTime":"2019-03-12T03:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T03:03:18.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"461f87c5b308fd3f09cc5068d5e53fb2140b4774","tid":1057539,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T03:03:18.000Z","msg":"德國經濟部長阿爾特邁爾（Peter Altmaier）月初表示，德國並不想禁止華為替其建造5G網絡。惟美國《華爾街日報》周一（11日）引述華府消息人士稱，美國駐德大使格雷內爾（Richard Grenell）上周已致函阿爾特邁爾，警告有關舉措將有代價。<br />\n<br />\n格雷內爾在信中引述副總統彭斯等人警告，德國政府若允許華為參與當地5G網絡建設，將影響美德情報部門間的情報互通。<br />\n<br />\n德國駐美大使館發言人韋勒（Matthias Wehler）其後證實有關消息，指阿爾特邁爾的確接獲過有關信件，但暫時未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n（美國有線新聞網）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190312/s00005/1552358075315/%E3%80%90%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%E3%80%91%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B-%E8%8B%A5%E7%94%A8%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99%E5%B0%87%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%A3%E5%83%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190312%2Fs00005%2F1552358075315%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E7%2594%25A8%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E5%2583%25B9&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6Lc0zXsqQl3D3Nzt16t%2FTIU%3D&h=9073a134\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190312%2Fs00005%2F1552358075315%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E7%2594%25A8%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%259C%2